<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 6.35pt 0cm 0.0001pt 68.85pt; text-indent: -19.6pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif;" align="left"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> i.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Tidak dapat melakukan transaksi.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 6.3pt 0cm 0.0001pt 68.85pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -22pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> ii.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Tidak dapat menerima dana.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 6.35pt 0cm 0.0001pt 68.85pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -24.4pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> iii.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Dapat mengaktifkan kembali.</span></p>
