<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -21.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> iv.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 6pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Apabila Pengguna memberikan informasi data yang tidak benar atau menyesatkan atau palsu atau fiktif baik saat melakukan registrasi maupun saat melakukan transaksi keuangan dalam Aplikasi AstraPay (transfer dana/pembayaran/pembelian/dll).</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -18.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> v.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 6pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Apabila terdapat dugaan penyalahgunaan AstraPay untuk kegiatan yang melanggar hukum.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -21.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> vi.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 6pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN" style="letter-spacing: -0.05pt;">Laporan Pengguna bahwa telepon seluler Pengguna hilang atau telah dicuri atau telah diretas.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -21.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> vii.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 5pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN" style="letter-spacing: -0.05pt;">Alasan lain yang merugikan Pengguna atau Kami, termasuk tindakan curang dan tindakan penipuan, dan/atau</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -24.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> viii.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 5pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Ketika Sistem Kami menangkap pola transaksi keuangan yang mencurigakan.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -21.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> ix.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 6pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Pihak lain yang melaporkan adanya tindakan mencurigakan dari akun tersebut disertai dengan bukti-bukti yang dianggap cukup untuk keperluan investigasi.</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin: 0cm 6.75pt 0.0001pt 62.85pt; text-indent: -18.1pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Arial MT', sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt;"> x.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 6pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="IN">Berdasarkan penilaian dan kewenangan kami sendiri atas validitas akun Pengguna.</span></p>
